text":"As also the high priest doth bear me witness, and all the estate of the elders: from whom also I received letters unto the brethren, and went to Damascus, to bring them which were there bound unto Jerusalem, for to be punished.","year":60},{"id":"recBYiQzxaRM86n92","ref":"Acts.22.6","text":"And it came to pass, that, as I made my journey, and was come nigh unto Damascus about noon, suddenly there shone from heaven a great light round about me.","year":60},{"id":"recLpSM8eWegqHZ0s","ref":"Acts.22.7","text":"And I fell unto the ground, and heard a voice saying unto me, Saul, Saul, why persecutest thou me?","year":60},{"id":"recgd060b8gwf9TPR","ref":"Acts.22.8","text":"And I answered, Who art thou, Lord? And he said unto me, I am Jesus of Nazareth, whom thou persecutest.","year":60}]}
